These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-1::.
4 different pets are kept: hamster, guinea-pig, horse, cat
1. the owner of the hamster is on the far left##1
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the owner of the horse##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Pet   | hamster | guinea-pig | horse | cat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-2::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, havana, prince, cain
1. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the havana-smoker##1
2. the cain-smoker is on the left of the prince-smoker##1
3. the prince-smoker is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Cigar   | havana | chaman | cain | prince |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-3::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, skateboard, ship, roller
1. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person driving the roller is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Transport   | motorbike | ship | skateboard | roller |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-4::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, trike, scooter, bus
