2. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left or right of the person driving the bus##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |  4  |
| Transport   | trike | snowmobile | bus | scooter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-5::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, baccarat, game, bolivar
1. the vegafina-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
2. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the game-smoker##1
3. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |    2    |  3   |     4      |
| Cigar   | bolivar | game | baccarat | vegafina |

