.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-6::.
City: hamburg, san-francisco, edinburgh, paris
1. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
2. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left or right of the person traveling to san-francisco##3
3. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
4. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3   |   4    |
| City   | hamburg | edinburgh | san-francisco | paris |

