2. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
3. the person who growsbellflower is on the left or right of the person who growstulip##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |    2     |   3   |   4    |
| Flower   | iris | aconite | bellflower | tulip |

