.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-9::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, cooking, filmmaking, drawing
1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##3
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
4. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |     3     |    4    |
| Hobby   | filmmaking | cooking | sudoku | drawing |

