1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is between the person who's hobby is baking and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##2
3. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##3
4. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks | skydiving | baking | woodworking |

