1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far left##1
2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in june##3
3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |   2    |     3      |   4    |
| Birthday   | march | june | october | november |

