.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-12::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, fantasy, comedy, thriller
1. the person watching comedy movies is between the person watching thriller movies and the person watching fantasy movies##2
2. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
3. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the person watching action movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |  3   |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy | comedy | thriller | action |

