.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-20::.
4 different games are played: backgammon, scrabble, snooker, chess
1. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person playing chess##1
2. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
3. the person playing chess is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3
4. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |  2   |   3   |  4   |
| Game   | snooker | scrabble | backgammon | chess |

 